 and direct about my boundaries.",\n  "conflict_repair_friendship_lessons": "i''ve learned that i tend to try to \"fix\" people when i don''t feel comfortable and i tend to fall into the people pleasing or over extending myself. But i don''t need to do that. i learned that it''s not important to have friends who i can have fun with",\n  "hobbies_interests_activities_interests": [\n    "Yoga/Pilates",\n    "Music (playing, creating, deeply listening)",\n    "Crafting (pottery, knitting, DIY, etc)",\n    "Cooking/Baking",\n    "Hosting gatherings (dinner parties, game nights)",\n    "Attending events (concerts, markets, etc)",\n    "Exploring local spots (cafes, shops)",\n    "Podcasts and documentaries",\n    "Philosophy and deep conversations",\n    "Tarot/oracle cards",\n    "Astrology",\n    "Other"\n  ],\n  "hobbies_interests_activities_interests_other_text": "anime",\n  "hobbies_interests_doing_vs_being": "Both",\n  "values_top_values": [\n    "Empathy",\n    "Creativity",\n    "Fun",\n    "Genuineness",\n    "Inclusiveness",\n    "Community",\n    "Passion",\n    "Self-awareness",\n    "Self-expression",\n    "Vulnerability"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_statements_resonate": [\n    "I appreciate friends who respect my need for space",\n    "Friends should challenge me to grow",\n    "Humor and laughter are essential to friendship"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_friendship_needs": [\n    "Emotional depth and vulnerability",\n    "Shared laughter and lightness",\n    "Non-judgment and acceptance",\n    "Genuineness"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_non_negotiables": "Laughter and Humor is so important to me as a person I also values empathy and respect",\n  "friendship_values_dealbreakers": "Friends who don''t listen to other people or who try to force things onto someone else",\n  "friendship_values_connection_language": [\n    "Quality time (hangouts, phone calls, etc)",\n    "Emotional Support (showing up in hard times, being a listening ear)",\n    "Gifts (items that remind them of you)"\n  ],\n  "logistics_connection_frequency": "Once a week",\n  "logistics_connection_type": "Primarily in-person connections",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word1": "Funny",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word2": "Weird (in the good way)",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word3": "Honest",\n  "wrapping_up_what_want_receive": "I truly am looking for a solid group of friends it''s always been my dream to roll deep or have a group chat and go somewhere and it be fun and we all get along etc",\n  "wrapping_up_gender_preference": "No preference",\n  "wrapping_up_age_preference": "similar age to me 24-32 (i''m 30(",\n  "wrapping_up_open_to_multiple_matches": [\n    "Yes, I''m open to connecting with multiple people",\n    "Yes, I''m open to connecting with multiple people"\n  ]\n}','\n',char(10)),0,NULL);
INSERT INTO assessment VALUES(7,15,replace('{\n  "tell_us_more_what_brings_you": "I''m transitioning into a new season, and though I have a very solid foundational friend group we are very spread out. I would love to curate some new friendships in the city as I approach thirty.",\n  "friendship_readiness_emotional_availability": "10",\n  "friendship_readiness_time_energy_capacity": "Good capacity (I''m ready to prioritize friendships)",\n  "friendship_readiness_friendship_intention": "I am open to friendships, but want to take it slow",\n  "friendship_readiness_personal_work": "Yes, I''ve worked through a lot in therapy/self-reflection",\n  "friendship_readiness_life_circumstances_details": "I am a very open friend in this current season. I have an open door policy in my home presently, prioritize my friends like family.",\n  "friendship_readiness_showing_up": "I feel like showing up is a case by case basis for what each friend needs at the time, but showing up is honestly doing what you can without sacrificing your own well-being.",\n  "personality_social_style_recharge_style": "3",\n  "personality_social_style_social_settings": "Share openly and engage actively with most people",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_0": "1",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_1": "4",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_2": "2",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_3": "3",\n  "personality_social_style_making_plans": "I prefer concrete plans with minimal wiggle room",\n  "personality_social_style_communication_preference": [\n    "Primarily in-person hangouts",\n    "Mix of everything/I''m flexible"\n  ],\n  "personality_social_style_texting_style": "Quick responder, love ongoing conversations",\n  "conflict_repair_conflict_response": "Address it directly and as soon as possible",\n  "conflict_repair_repair_looks_like": [\n    "A direct conversation about what happened",\n    "Quality time together to reconnect",\n    "Acts of care and presence",\n    "Acknowledgement of impact and sincere apology"\n  ],\n  "conflict_repair_flaky_friend_scenario": "Stay curious and check in:",\n  "conflict_repair_feedback_comfort": "5",\n  "conflict_repair_boundary_setting": "I am clear and direct about my boundaries.",\n  "conflict_repair_friendship_lessons": "I notice I put my desires to the side to prioritize friendships, and that hurts both sides. I''ve learned to balance myself and others, and those that don''t align will start to stand out.",\n  "hobbies_interests_activities_interests": [\n    "Hiking/nature walks",\n    "Yoga/Pilates",\n    "Writing (journaling, poetry, books)",\n    "Visual arts (painting, drawing, photography)",\n    "Music (playing, creating, deeply listening)",\n    "Crafting (pottery, knitting, DIY, etc)",\n    "Cooking/Baking",\n    "Fashion/Styling",\n    "Hosting gatherings (dinner parties, game nights)",\n    "Book clubs or discussion groups",\n    "Volunteering/advocacy",\n    "Attending events (concerts, markets, etc)",\n    "Exploring local spots (cafes, shops)",\n    "Reading (fiction, non-fiction, audiobooks)",\n    "Philosophy and deep conversations",\n    "Learning new skills",\n    "Writing and reflection",\n    "Activism and social change",\n    "Astrology",\n    "Religious gatherings (temple/church/mosque, etc)",\n    "Therapy/personal growth work",\n    "Nature connection and grounding",\n    "Medicinal herbs/substances"\n  ],\n  "hobbies_interests_doing_vs_being": "Both",\n  "values_top_values": [\n    "Beauty",\n    "Career",\n    "Creativity",\n    "Health",\n    "Fun",\n    "Generosity",\n    "Integrity",\n    "Leadership",\n    "Self-awareness",\n    "Self-expression"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_statements_resonate": [\n    "Friendship is about celebrating each other''s wins",\n    "I value reliability and follow-through",\n    "Humor and laughter are essential to friendship"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_friendship_needs": [\n    "Emotional depth and vulnerability",\n    "Shared laughter and lightness",\n    "Intellectual stimulation",\n    "Mutual support during hard times",\n    "Celebration of wins and joys",\n    "Accountability and growth",\n    "Consistency and reliability",\n    "Genuineness",\n    "Adventure and new experiences"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_non_negotiables": "must love pets, music, and getting dressed up!",\n  "friendship_values_dealbreakers": "insecure, unambitious, etc. I don''t like to gossip or talk about people just to demean them",\n  "friendship_values_connection_language": [\n    "Quality time (hangouts, phone calls, etc)",\n    "Words of affirmation (encouragement, posts about you)",\n    "Emotional Support (showing up in hard times, being a listening ear)"\n  ],\n  "logistics_connection_frequency": "Quality over quantity \u2013 frequency matters less than depth",\n  "logistics_connection_type": "Mix of both",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word1": "ambitious",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word2": "confident",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word3": "genuine",\n  "wrapping_up_what_want_receive": "my biggest thing is to receive genuine love and support, and grow my community because everyone has different roles to make the community thrive.",\n  "wrapping_up_gender_preference": "No preference",\n  "wrapping_up_age_preference": "26-35",\n  "wrapping_up_open_to_multiple_matches": [\n    "Yes, I''m open to connecting with multiple people",\n    "Yes, I''m open to connecting with multiple people"\n  ]\n}','\n',char(10)),0,NULL);
INSERT INTO assessment VALUES(8,17,replace('{\n  "tell_us_more_what_brings_you": "I feel like I have 2 friends, both of whom I work with. I got out of a toxic relationship and find it hard to relate to other people and bond. I\u2019m so easy going but I work a lot and I work 2nd shift so I think that plays a part",\n  "friendship_readiness_emotional_availability": "8",\n  "friendship_readiness_time_energy_capacity": "Moderate capacity (I can make time, but need flexibility)",\n  "friendship_readiness_friendship_intention": "I am actively seeking close, intimate friendships",\n  "friendship_readiness_personal_work": "I am actively working on it now",\n  "friendship_readiness_life_circumstances": "Ending a significant relationship",\n  "friendship_readiness_life_circumstances_details": "People who know how to communicate would be great too.",\n  "friendship_readiness_showing_up": "Being there to vent, making time for each other, prioritizing communication",\n  "personality_social_style_recharge_style": "2",\n  "personality_social_style_social_settings": "I''m quiet at first but warm up over time",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_0": "2",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_1": "1",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_2": "4",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_3": "3",\n  "personality_social_style_making_plans": "I like having loose plans but staying flexible",\n  "personality_social_style_communication_preference": [\n    "Texting throughout the day",\n    "Voice notes"\n  ],\n  "personality_social_style_texting_style": "Quick responder, love ongoing conversations",\n  "conflict_repair_conflict_response": "Address it directly and as soon as possible",\n  "conflict_repair_repair_looks_like": [\n    "A direct conversation about what happened",\n    "Quality time together to reconnect",\n    "Acts of care and presence",\n    "Acknowledgement of impact and sincere apology"\n  ],\n  "conflict_repair_flaky_friend_scenario": "Set a boundary:",\n  "conflict_repair_feedback_comfort": "5",\n  "conflict_repair_boundary_setting": "It depends on the friendship",\n  "conflict_repair_friendship_lessons": "I\u2019m an anxious attachment which sucks, I need people to be upfront and honest with me or I get anxious. I over communicate and I don\u2019t do well with people who lack that.",\n  "hobbies_interests_activities_interests": [\n    "Hiking/nature walks",\n    "Yoga/Pilates",\n    "Rock climbing/adventure sports",\n    "Crafting (pottery, knitting, DIY, etc)",\n    "Cooking/Baking",\n    "Fashion/Styling",\n    "Attending events (concerts, markets, etc)",\n    "Exploring local spots (cafes, shops)",\n    "Reading (fiction, non-fiction, audiobooks)",\n    "Learning new skills"\n  ],\n  "hobbies_interests_doing_vs_being": "Doing: I love activities, adventures, and experiences with friends",\n  "values_top_values": [\n    "Empathy",\n    "Fun",\n    "Genuineness",\n    "Fulfillment",\n    "Trust",\n    "Loyalty",\n    "Self-awareness",\n    "Stability",\n    "Vulnerability"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_statements_resonate": [\n    "Friendship is about celebrating each other''s wins",\n    "Humor and laughter are essential to friendship",\n    "I need friends who can hold space for my emotions"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_friendship_needs": [\n    "Mutual support during hard times",\n    "Non-judgment and acceptance",\n    "Consistency and reliability",\n    "Peaceful, easy presence"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_non_negotiables": "Acceptance, same sense of humor, non judgmental, go with the flow, communicative",\n  "friendship_values_dealbreakers": "Ghosting, lying, going after an ex or someone I\u2019m talking to, drugs",\n  "friendship_values_connection_language": [\n    "Quality time (hangouts, phone calls, etc)",\n    "Words of affirmation (encouragement, posts about you)",\n    "Emotional Support (showing up in hard times, being a listening ear)"\n  ],\n  "logistics_connection_frequency": "Once a week",\n  "logistics_connection_type": "Primarily in-person connections",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word1": "Loyal",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word2": "Kind",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word3": "Accepting",\n  "wrapping_up_what_want_receive": "More meaningful friendships, find new people and new hobbies",\n  "wrapping_up_gender_preference": "No preference",\n  "wrapping_up_age_preference": "Similar to me, I\u2019m 29, maybe 26-34",\n  "wrapping_up_open_to_multiple_matches": [\n    "Yes, I''m open to connecting with multiple people",\n    "Yes, I''m open to connecting with multiple people"\n  ]\n}','\n',char(10)),1,NULL);
INSERT INTO assessment VALUES(9,20,replace('{\n  "tell_us_more_what_brings_you": "Iris!! But also, I\u2019m just in a stage of my life where I want to meet new people and gain some new friends! I\u2019ve been in Charlotte for 3 years and I really want to put myself out there more intentionally now that I\u2019m not fully in survival mode (lol)!",\n  "friendship_readiness_emotional_availability": "9",\n  "friendship_readiness_time_energy_capacity": "Good capacity (I''m ready to prioritize friendships)",\n  "friendship_readiness_friendship_intention": "I am actively seeking close, intimate friendships",\n  "friendship_readiness_personal_work": "Yes, I''ve worked through a lot in therapy/self-reflection",\n  "friendship_readiness_life_circumstances": "N/A",\n  "friendship_readiness_life_circumstances_details": "",\n  "friendship_readiness_showing_up": "I think it\u2019s really about consistency. Being willing to keep trying to connect with one another is important to me. And listening skills. Showing up requires ensuring that the other person feels seen.",\n  "personality_social_style_recharge_style": "3",\n  "personality_social_style_social_settings": "Share openly and engage actively with most people",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_0": "4",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_1": "3",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_2": "2",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_3": "1",\n  "personality_social_style_making_plans": "I like having loose plans but staying flexible",\n  "personality_social_style_communication_preference": [\n    "Texting throughout the day",\n    "Video calls"\n  ],\n  "personality_social_style_texting_style": "Thoughtful but slow to respond (hours to days)",\n  "conflict_repair_conflict_response": "Need time to process before I am ready to discuss",\n  "conflict_repair_repair_looks_like": [\n    "A direct conversation about what happened",\n    "Quality time together to reconnect",\n    "Acknowledgement of impact and sincere apology",\n    "Humor and lightness to ease back in"\n  ],\n  "conflict_repair_flaky_friend_scenario": "Stay curious and check in:",\n  "conflict_repair_feedback_comfort": "4",\n  "conflict_repair_boundary_setting": "It depends on the friendship",\n  "conflict_repair_friendship_lessons": "I think I had a tendency to bottle things up and then become emotionally distant or agitated if a friend\u2019s repeated behavior bothered me. Now, I try to lean more towards having a conversation when I\u2019m calmer, and even if I feel like we might stumble through the conversation to clear the air (I may not get all my words right, neither may the other person), I\u2019m much more confident when it comes to addressing friction now. And, I\u2019ve been working to take things less personally, which has also helped a lot!",\n  "hobbies_interests_activities_interests": [\n    "Hiking/nature walks",\n    "Yoga/Pilates",\n    "Dancing (salsa, pole, aerial, casual, etc)",\n    "Sports (playing or watching)",\n    "Writing (journaling, poetry, books)",\n    "Crafting (pottery, knitting, DIY, etc)",\n    "Cooking/Baking",\n    "Hosting gatherings (dinner parties, game nights)",\n    "Book clubs or discussion groups",\n    "Volunteering/advocacy",\n    "Attending events (concerts, markets, etc)",\n    "Reading (fiction, non-fiction, audiobooks)",\n    "Podcasts and documentaries",\n    "Learning new skills",\n    "Activism and social change",\n    "Meditation/mindfulness",\n    "Astrology",\n    "Religious gatherings (temple/church/mosque, etc)",\n    "Therapy/personal growth work"\n  ],\n  "hobbies_interests_doing_vs_being": "Both",\n  "values_top_values": [\n    "Social Justice",\n    "Empathy",\n    "Fun",\n    "Genuineness",\n    "Gratitude",\n    "Community",\n    "Love",\n    "Resilience",\n    "Self-awareness",\n    "Stability"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_statements_resonate": [\n    "Friendship is about celebrating each other''s wins",\n    "Humor and laughter are essential to friendship",\n    "Mutual effort and reciprocity matters to me"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_friendship_needs": [\n    "Shared laughter and lightness",\n    "Celebration of wins and joys",\n    "Consistency and reliability",\n    "Genuineness"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_non_negotiables": "I think consistency, willingness to try (whether it\u2019s a hobby or an actual behavior when it comes to showing up for someone), self-awareness, and joy are most important to me.",\n  "friendship_values_dealbreakers": "Unwillingness to self-examine and lack of respect for boundaries.",\n  "friendship_values_connection_language": [\n    "Quality time (hangouts, phone calls, etc)",\n    "Words of affirmation (encouragement, posts about you)",\n    "Emotional Support (showing up in hard times, being a listening ear)"\n  ],\n  "logistics_connection_frequency": "Once a week",\n  "logistics_connection_type": "Primarily in-person connections",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word1": "Empathetic",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word2": "Joyful",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word3": "Reliable",\n  "wrapping_up_what_want_receive": "I\u2019d like to receive a listening ear, an adventure buddy, a fellow giggler, and someone who I can celebrate life\u2019s joys alongside (and navigate life\u2019s burdens with).",\n  "wrapping_up_gender_preference": "No preference",\n  "wrapping_up_age_preference": "Similar age to me (in the range of 24-32)",\n  "wrapping_up_open_to_multiple_matches": [\n    "Yes, I''m open to connecting with multiple people",\n    "Yes, I''m open to connecting with multiple people"\n  ]\n}','\n',char(10)),1,NULL);
INSERT INTO assessment VALUES(10,24,replace('{\n  "tell_us_more_what_brings_you": "I have lived in Charlotte for around 5 years now and love it! Always looking for ways to support the community and connect with people !",\n  "friendship_readiness_emotional_availability": "10",\n  "friendship_readiness_time_energy_capacity": "Moderate capacity (I can make time, but need flexibility)",\n  "friendship_readiness_friendship_intention": "I would like casual connections that could grow naturally over time",\n  "friendship_readiness_personal_work": "Yes, I''ve worked through a lot in therapy/self-reflection",\n  "friendship_readiness_life_circumstances": "Major career transition",\n  "friendship_readiness_life_circumstances_details": "",\n  "friendship_readiness_showing_up": "Showing up in a friendship to me is not necessarily the amount of time you can give it\u2019s the quality of time you can give. It\u2019s important to me to have friends that show up for each other but also understand that life is hectic!",\n  "personality_social_style_recharge_style": "3",\n  "personality_social_style_social_settings": "Share openly and engage actively with most people",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_0": "4",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_1": "2",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_2": "3",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_3": "1",\n  "personality_social_style_making_plans": "I like having loose plans but staying flexible",\n  "personality_social_style_communication_preference": [\n    "Phone calls",\n    "Primarily in-person hangouts"\n  ],\n  "personality_social_style_texting_style": "Thoughtful but slow to respond (hours to days)",\n  "conflict_repair_conflict_response": "Address it directly and as soon as possible",\n  "conflict_repair_repair_looks_like": [\n    "A direct conversation about what happened",\n    "Time and space before reconnecting"\n  ],\n  "conflict_repair_flaky_friend_scenario": "Set a boundary:",\n  "conflict_repair_feedback_comfort": "4",\n  "conflict_repair_boundary_setting": "I struggle with boundaries and often overextend",\n  "conflict_repair_friendship_lessons": "It is better to take a minute before responding. Address the problem and let it go",\n  "hobbies_interests_activities_interests": [\n    "Hiking/nature walks",\n    "Running/Cycling",\n    "Sports (playing or watching)",\n    "Cooking/Baking",\n    "Fashion/Styling",\n    "Hosting gatherings (dinner parties, game nights)",\n    "Book clubs or discussion groups",\n    "Attending events (concerts, markets, etc)",\n    "Exploring local spots (cafes, shops)",\n    "Reading (fiction, non-fiction, audiobooks)",\n    "Podcasts and documentaries",\n    "Therapy/personal growth work"\n  ],\n  "hobbies_interests_doing_vs_being": "Both",\n  "values_top_values": [\n    "Ambition",\n    "Career",\n    "Health",\n    "Fun",\n    "Generosity",\n    "Fulfillment",\n    "Growth",\n    "Trust",\n    "Independence",\n    "Leadership"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_statements_resonate": [\n    "Friendship is about celebrating each other''s wins",\n    "I value reliability and follow-through",\n    "Humor and laughter are essential to friendship"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_friendship_needs": [\n    "Emotional depth and vulnerability",\n    "Shared laughter and lightness",\n    "Intellectual stimulation",\n    "Mutual support during hard times",\n    "Celebration of wins and joys",\n    "Accountability and growth",\n    "Non-judgment and acceptance",\n    "Consistency and reliability",\n    "Genuineness",\n    "Adventure and new experiences",\n    "Peaceful, easy presence"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_non_negotiables": "Respect for boundaries and time and no judgment",\n  "friendship_values_dealbreakers": "Negativity, selfishness",\n  "friendship_values_connection_language": "Quality time (hangouts, phone calls, etc)",\n  "logistics_connection_frequency": "Quality over quantity \u2013 frequency matters less than depth",\n  "logistics_connection_type": "Primarily in-person connections",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word1": "Fun",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word2": "Intelligent",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word3": "Genuine",\n  "wrapping_up_what_want_receive": "Genuine support and activities",\n  "wrapping_up_gender_preference": "Woman",\n  "wrapping_up_age_preference": "Similar age to me",\n  "wrapping_up_open_to_multiple_matches": [\n    "Yes, I''m open to connecting with multiple people",\n    "Yes, I''m open to connecting with multiple people"\n  ]\n}','\n',char(10)),1,NULL);
INSERT INTO assessment VALUES(11,25,replace('{\n  "tell_us_more_what_brings_you": "I love meeting new people and making new friends. Getting matched up with a friend sounds fun and I am interested to try it out.",\n  "friendship_readiness_emotional_availability": "8",\n  "friendship_readiness_time_energy_capacity": "Moderate capacity (I can make time, but need flexibility)",\n  "friendship_readiness_friendship_intention": "I am open to friendships, but want to take it slow",\n  "friendship_readiness_personal_work": "I am actively working on it now",\n  "friendship_readiness_life_circumstances": "Other",\n  "friendship_readiness_life_circumstances_other_text": "I am currently in graduate school, working full time, obtaining hours to sit for the BCBA board exam, and planning a wedding. I am open to meeting new friends and would like to build friendships but need some flexibility with scheduling and making plans.",\n  "friendship_readiness_life_circumstances_details": "",\n  "friendship_readiness_showing_up": "Being available for friends when they need you, making time to connect either in person or through phone calls, texts, video calls\u2026 ect. Life is busy and things happen but keeping in touch is important.",\n  "personality_social_style_recharge_style": "3",\n  "personality_social_style_social_settings": "Observe, listen deeply, and engage selectively",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_0": "2",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_1": "3",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_2": "4",\n  "personality_social_style_ideal_hangout_3": "1",\n  "personality_social_style_making_plans": "I like having loose plans but staying flexible",\n  "personality_social_style_communication_preference": [\n    "Texting throughout the day",\n    "Mix of everything/I''m flexible"\n  ],\n  "personality_social_style_texting_style": "Thoughtful but slow to respond (hours to days)",\n  "conflict_repair_conflict_response": "Address it directly and as soon as possible",\n  "conflict_repair_repair_looks_like": "A direct conversation about what happened",\n  "conflict_repair_flaky_friend_scenario": "Address it directly:",\n  "conflict_repair_feedback_comfort": "5",\n  "conflict_repair_boundary_setting": "It depends on the friendship",\n  "conflict_repair_friendship_lessons": "I like to address conflict directly and try to move past, I get uncomfortable with conflict but I acknowledge the importance of direct communication to move past it. But I don\u2019t push communication if the other person is pulling back. I respect others needs and if they are not reciprocating my attempts to directly approach the issue I will pull back and wait for them to approach me.",\n  "hobbies_interests_activities_interests": [\n    "Yoga/Pilates",\n    "Dancing (salsa, pole, aerial, casual, etc)",\n    "Visual arts (painting, drawing, photography)",\n    "Music (playing, creating, deeply listening)",\n    "Crafting (pottery, knitting, DIY, etc)",\n    "Cooking/Baking",\n    "Hosting gatherings (dinner parties, game nights)",\n    "Volunteering/advocacy",\n    "Attending events (concerts, markets, etc)",\n    "Exploring local spots (cafes, shops)",\n    "Podcasts and documentaries",\n    "Philosophy and deep conversations",\n    "Learning new skills",\n    "Activism and social change",\n    "Meditation/mindfulness",\n    "Tarot/oracle cards",\n    "Astrology",\n    "Therapy/personal growth work"\n  ],\n  "hobbies_interests_doing_vs_being": "Both",\n  "values_top_values": [\n    "Activism",\n    "Social Justice",\n    "Fun",\n    "Inclusiveness",\n    "Integrity",\n    "Loyalty",\n    "Love",\n    "Self-awareness",\n    "Uniqueness",\n    "Vulnerability"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_statements_resonate": [\n    "Friends should be able to have difficult conversations",\n    "Friendship is about celebrating each other''s wins",\n    "I value friends who share my worldview and values"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_friendship_needs": [\n    "Emotional depth and vulnerability",\n    "Mutual support during hard times",\n    "Celebration of wins and joys",\n    "Accountability and growth",\n    "Non-judgment and acceptance",\n    "Consistency and reliability",\n    "Genuineness",\n    "Adventure and new experiences"\n  ],\n  "friendship_values_non_negotiables": "Similar values and morals, openness, respect, compassion, communication,",\n  "friendship_values_dealbreakers": "Hatefulness, bigotry, poor communication skills, selfishness, close minded,",\n  "friendship_values_connection_language": [\n    "Quality time (hangouts, phone calls, etc)",\n    "Words of affirmation (encouragement, posts about you)",\n    "Emotional Support (showing up in hard times, being a listening ear)"\n  ],\n  "logistics_connection_frequency": "I am open",\n  "logistics_connection_type": "Mix of both",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word1": "Kind",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word2": "Loyal",\n  "wrapping_up_ideal_friend_words_word3": "Self aware",\n  "wrapping_up_what_want_receive": "Support, connections, love, respect, loyalty",\n  "wrapping_up_gender_preference": [\n    "Woman",\n    "Non-binary"\n  ],\n  "wrapping_up_age_preference": "25-33",\n  "wrapping_up_open_to_multiple_matches": [\n    "Yes, I''m open to connecting with multiple people",\n    "Yes, I''m open to connecting with multiple people"\n  ]\n}','\n',char(10)),1,18);
