INSERT INTO "match" VALUES(21,48,19,26,21,'finalized','Done',NULL,'2026-01-08 05:30:32.990375','2026-01-11 09:34:11.551992',replace('Hi Sami,\n\nI''m so excited to introduce you to Courtney (she/her)! After carefully reviewing both of your assessments, I have a really good feeling about this match.\n\nHere''s why I think you two will connect:\n\nYou both ranked adventure, peace, and similar political views in your top values, and expressed wanting a connection where you can both give each other reciprocal energy, but also where you can be yourself free from judgment!  \n\nI noticed that Courtney, you mentioned wanting a friend who is open-minded and empathetic, and Sami, you described yourself as someone who values self-awareness, openness, and the ability to put yourself in the other person''s shoes. That feels like a beautiful alignment. \n\nSome fun overlaps:\n• You both are witchy, valuing spirituality via nature, tarot, astrology, etc\n• You both enjoy quality time, words of affirmations, and emotional support in a friendship \n• You both enjoy hiking/nature walks, dancing, crafting, deep conversations, and activism\n\nA gentle awareness: Sami, you mentioned wanting to address any conflict as soon as possible, and Courtney, you prefer taking the time to process before you have a discussion. This could actually be a beautiful balance if you both communicate openly about your needs!\n\nNext steps: I''ve sent this same message to both of you with each other''s contact info. I encourage you to reach out within the next few days to set up a casual first meeting—coffee, a walk, whatever feels right. You both also RSVP''d for our launch party this Sunday at 1 PM, so this would be a perfect space to start out! :~) \n\nHere are a few more ideas from the Three of Cups team:\n• Crafts and a picnic at Freedom Park\n• Tarot readings together \n• Finding a space to volunteer in together \n\nContact info:\n• Courtney (she/her) - courtneymwyche@gmail.com\n\nI''m rooting for yo