INSERT INTO "match" VALUES(22,11,53,4,31,'finalized','Done',NULL,'2026-01-09 20:16:19.974134','2026-01-11 09:32:06.585848',replace('Hi Nathalia,\n\nI''m so excited to introduce you to Melissa (she/her)! After carefully reviewing both of your assessments, I have a really good feeling about this match.\n\nHere''s why I think you two will connect:\n\nYou both ranked fun in your top values, and expressed wanting a more casual connection where you can take your time getting to know each other. You are both also clear and direct about your boundaries! \n\nI noticed that Nathalia, you mentioned wanting a friend who is peaceful, mindful, and makes time to connect with their friends and Melissa, you described yourself as someone who values good energy, kind, and makes time to connect with their friends. That feels like a beautiful alignment. \n\nSome fun overlaps:\n• You both enjoy quality time and celebrating each other\n• You both enjoy yoga/pilates, dancing, crafting, astrology, nature, mindfulness, and holistic health practices such as therapy and energy work \n\nA gentle awareness: Nathalia, you mentioned preferring concrete plans, and Melissa, you prefer having loose plans with flexibility. This could actually be a beautiful balance if you both communicate openly about your needs!\n\nNext steps: I''ve sent this same message to both of you with each other''s contact info. I encourage you to reach out within the next few days to set up a casual first meeting—coffee, a walk, whatever feels right. You both also RSVP''d for our launch party this Sunday at 1 PM, so this would be a perfect space to start out! :~) \n\nHere are a few more ideas from the Three of Cups team:\n• Taking a yoga class together \n• Going dancing together whether at an event or a studio \n• Learn a new skill together \n\nContact info:\n• Melissa (she/her) - madunn4@gmail.com\n\nI''m rooting for you both! Remember, not every match will become a lifelong friendship, and that''s okay. Stay open, be yourselves, and see what unfolds. See you two on Sunday!\n\n\nWith so much hope for beautiful connection,\n\nIris and the Three of Cups Team 🌟','\n',char(10)),NULL);
