INSERT INTO "match" VALUES(32,25,72,11,47,'finalized',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-09 20:21:38.101836','2026-01-11 10:15:20.137442',replace('Hi Madison and Chelsea,\n\nI''m so excited to introduce you both to each other! Madison, meet Chelsea (she/her)! Chelsea, meet Madison (she/her)! After carefully reviewing both of your assessments, I have a really good feeling about this match. \n\nHere''s why I think you two will connect:\n\nYou both expressed being open to friendships where you can also take your time. You both also ranked fun, loyalty, and justice as your top values, and outside of in-person hangs, you both prefer texting (or a mix of it all) and are thoughtful, but take your time to respond to texts. \n\nI noticed that Madison, you are seeking a friend you can just exist with -- someone who is understanding, not judgmental, funny, and steady. Chelsea, you are looking for a friend who is kind, loyal, reliable, and open-minded. This feels like a beautiful pairing! \n\nSome fun overlaps:\n• You both value people''s moral compass when it comes to friendship, and do not stand for any form of bigotry\n• You both enjoy dancing, music, astrology, tarot, and personal growth whether it be self/community-directed or therapy\n• You both value quality time, emotional support, and words of affirmation\n\n\nA gentle awareness: Chelsea, you are comfortable with addressing issues directly, but also honor people''s need to process before discussing, and Madison, confrontation has been hard in the past, but you are actively working on speaking more freely in your friendships. This could actually be a wonderful balance if navigated with openness, understanding, and intentionality. Sometimes, we need the space to practice speaking up in order for us to be able to feel safe while being direct. \n\nNext steps: I''ve sent this same message to both of you with each other''s contact info. I encourage you to reach out within the next few days to set up a casual first meeting—coffee, a walk, wh