et up a casual first meeting—coffee, a walk, whatever feels right. You both also RSVP''d for our launch party this Sunday at 1 PM, so this would be a perfect space to start out! :~) \n\nHere are a few more ideas from the Three of Cups team:\n• Tarot and chill date at the park\n• Going out dancing\n• Take a walk around Freedom Park\n\nContact info:\n• Emma (she/they) -  emhallbils@gmail.com\n\nI''m rooting for you both! Remember, not every match will become a lifelong friendship, and that''s okay. Stay open, be yourselves, and see what unfolds. See you two on Sunday!\n\n\nWith so much hope for beautiful connection,\n\nIris and the Three of Cups Team 🌟','\n',char(10)));
