ith so much hope for beautiful connection,\n\nIris and The Three of Cups Team 🌟','\n',char(10)),replace('Hi Asha and Bryia,\n\nI''m so excited to introduce you both to each other! Bryia, meet Asha (she/her)! Asha, meet Bryia (she/her)! After carefully reviewing both of your assessments, I have a really good feeling about this match.\n\nHere''s why I think you two will connect:\n\nYou both ranked trust, vulnerability, and love in your top values and have a desire for a friendship where you feel mutually supported. \n\nI noticed that Asha, you mentioned desiring a friendship that holds you accountable, and Bryia, you mentioned desiring a friendship that prioritizes growth and accountability. That feels like a beautiful alignment. \n\nSome fun overlaps:\n• You both prefer quality time, physical touch, and emotional support in friendships \n• You both enjoy hiking/walks, spirituality, and reading\n• You both value vulnerability, reciprocity, and being challenged to grow \n\nA gentle awareness: Asha, you are looking for casual connections that could grow naturally over time, and Bryia, you are looking for more intimate and close friendships. This could actually be a great fit if both of you utilize healthy communication and patience. \n\nNext steps: I''ve sent this same message to both of you with each other''s contact info. I encourage you to reach out within the next few days to set up a casual first meeting—coffee, a walk, whatever feels right. You both also RSVP''d for our event tomorrow, so this will be a great start! :~) \n\nHere are a few more ideas from the Three of Cups team:\n• Do a tarot pull for each other\n• Start a new book together\n• Exchange playlists\n\nContact info:\n• You both are CC''d on this email, so feel free to reach out individually! \n\nI''m rooting for you both! Remember, not every match will become a lifelong friendship, and that''s okay. Stay open, be yourselves, and see what unfolds. See you two on Sunday!\n\n\nWith so much hope for beauti