ever feels right. You both also RSVP''d for our event tomorrow, so this will be a great start! :~)  \n\nHere are a few more ideas from the Three of Cups team:\n• Share your top 5 artists with each other \n• Craft date at the park \n• Take turns sharing hobbies with each other \n\nContact info:\n• You both are CC''d on this email, so feel free to reach out individually! \n\nI''m rooting for you both! Remember, not every match will become a lifelong friendship, and that''s okay. Stay open, be yourselves, and see what unfolds. See you two tomorrow!\n\n\nWith so much hope for beautiful connection,\n\nIris and The Three of Cups Team 🌟','\n',char(10)));
INSERT INTO "match" VALUES(84,129,109,84,68,'finalized',NULL,NULL,'2026-03-28 03:38:11.426791','2026-03-28 03:38:21.789117',replace('Hi Laura and Dominique,\n\nI''m so excited to introduce you both to each other! Dominique, meet Laura (she/her)! Laura meet Dominique (she/her)! After carefully reviewing both of your assessments, I have a really good feeling about this match.\n\nHere''s why I think you two will connect:\n\nYou both are actively seeking new friendships and are ready to invest in building something genuine and lasting. \n\nSome fun overlaps:\n• You both love cooking/baking, attending events, exploring local spots, reading, and visual arts.\n• You both value honesty, genuineness, and have punctuality as a non-negotiable. \n• You both need time to process before addressing conflict and value a direct conversation and sincere apology to repair. \n\nA gentle awareness:  Dominique, you''ve shared that too much sarcasm can be a lot for you, and Laura, your humor and wit are such a beautiful part of who you are. This could be a wonderful opportunity to learn each other''s communication styles with curiosity and an open heart! \n\nNext steps: I''ve sent this same message to both of you with each other''s contact info. I encourage you to reach out within the next few days to set up a casual first meeting—coffee, a walk, whatever feels right. You both also RSVP''d for our event tomorrow, so this will be a great start! :~) \n\nHere are a few more ideas from the Three of Cups team:\n• Find a new hobby to do together\n• Find a cause to contribute to \n• Take turns sharing hobbies \n\nContact info:\n• You both are CC''d on this email, so feel free to reach out individually! \n\nI''m rooting for you both! Remember, not every match will become a lifelong friendship, and that''s okay. Stay open, be yourselves, and see what unfolds. See you two tomorrow!\n\n\nWith so much hope for beautiful connection,\n\nIris and The Three of Cups Team 🌟','\n',char(10)),replace('Hi Laur