INSERT INTO "match" VALUES(85,99,18,63,55,'finalized',NULL,NULL,'2026-03-28 03:47:18.329922','2026-03-28 03:47:40.177447',replace('Hi Alex and Morgan,\n\nI''m so excited to introduce you both to each other! Alex, meet Morgan (they/them but any pronouns)! Morgan, meet Alex (she/her)! After carefully reviewing both of your assessments, I have a really good feeling about this match.\n\nHere''s why I think you two will connect:\n\nYou both ranked social justice and empathy in your top values. \n\nI noticed that Alex, you mentioned desiring a friendship that is actively anti-racist and queer-affirming, and Morgan, you mentioned desiring a friendship that is willing to have hard conversations and willing to acknowledge the oppressive systems we live in! This feels like a great match. \n\nSome fun overlaps:\n• You both enjoy dancing, writing, music, crafts, activism, energy/holistic practices, and nature connection and grounding \n• You both enjoy quality time with friends and words of affirmations\n• You both value laughter and growth in friendships\n\nNext steps: I''ve sent this same message to both of you with each other''s contact info. I encourage you to reach out within the next few days to set up a casual first meeting—coffee, a walk, whatever feels right. You both also RSVP''d for our event tomorrow, so this will be a great start! :~) \n\nHere are a few more ideas from the Three of Cups team:\n• Go out dancing together (dance classes, @girlsroomclt or @petras)\n• Exchange playlists    \n• Do a craft in the park together \n\nContact info:\n• You both are CC''d on this email, so feel free to reach out individually! \n\nI''m rooting for you both! Remember, not every match will become a lifelong friendship, and that''s okay. Stay open, be yourselves, and see what unfolds. See you two tomorrow!\n\n\nWith so much hope for beautiful connection,\n\nThe Three of Cups Team 🌟','\n',char(10)),replace('Hi Alex and Morgan,\n\nI''m so excited to introduce you both to each other! 