INSERT INTO "match" VALUES(86,145,110,97,69,'finalized',NULL,NULL,'2026-03-28 15:54:24.104101','2026-03-28 15:54:33.465236',replace('Hi Bug and Grey,\n\nI''m so excited to introduce you both to each other! Grey, meet Bug (they/he)! Bug, meet Grey (they/them)! After carefully reviewing both of your assessments, I have a really good feeling about this match.\n\nHere''s why I think you two will connect:\n\nYou both desire a friendship that is intimate, and close -- one with mutual effort and reciprocity. You also both are looking for a friendship that is consistent, kind, and warm. \n\nSome fun overlaps:\n• You both enjoy activism and social change, fashion, philosophy and deep conversations, and different modes of creativity (Bug loves to write and Grey loves to craft!) \n• You both enjoy quality time and emotional support from friends \n• You both prefer one-on-one conversations rather than large gatherings \n\nNext steps: I''ve sent this same message to both of you with each other''s contact info. I encourage you to reach out within the next few days to set up a casual first meeting—coffee, a walk, whatever feels right. You both also RSVP''d for our event tomorrow, so this will be a great start! :~) \n\nHere are a few more ideas from the Three of Cups team:\n• Spend time sharing what friendship means to you in this season of your lives \n• Take turns sharing writings and art pieces together \n• Find a cause to support while also supporting each other  \n\nContact info:\n• You both are CC''d on this email, so feel free to reach out individually! \n\nI''m rooting for you both! Remember, not every match will become a lifelong friendship, and that''s okay. Stay open, be yourselves, and see what unfolds. See you two soon! \n\n\nWith so much hope for beautiful connection,\n\nIris and The Three of Cups Team 🌟','\n',char(10)),replace('Hi Bug and Grey,\n\nI''m so excited to introduce you both to each other! Grey, meet Bug (they/he)! Bug, meet Grey (they/them)! After carefull